description: Redevelopment of site to provide a total of 118 residential units and 1037sqm of commercial floor space together with a medical centre and community hall comprising a part 6-storey, part 8-storey block of 96 self contained flats (31 x 1-bed, 57 x 2-bed 8 x 3-bed) with balconies to front, rear and side, three blocks of five 4-bed 3-storey terrace houses and 1 block of 7 x 3-bed, 2-storey terraced houses, alterations to access from Alpha Road, landscaping works, 26 car parking spaces and 179 cycle parking spaces and a change of use of car park at Trafalgar Place from public to private parking.
